      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row386337#s2",
      "text": "Male with HD dependent ESRD, CAD s/p MI, non-ischemic    CMY (EF 35-40%)  who presents w/ 3day h/o malaise- Pt was found down on    floor @ [**Hospital3 **] confused & disoriented- Initially, was    hyperkalemic w/ backpain and hemodynamically [**Hospital 10157**] transferred to ICU    from floor on [**2117-8-26**] for suspicion of GPC sepsis from HD line and    hypotension-    HD tunnel cath D/C    Sepsis without organ dysfunction    Assessment:    GPC bacterimia per blood cultures- + mult abcessesses seen on lung CT-    WBC 21.3 trending up (17.3)- T max 100.1 PO-    Action:    New R fem dialysis cath inserted in IR- repeat chest CT done- zosyn    D/C d- con t on vanco & levetiracetam."
    },
